eadObject(Input input, Class<T> type) {\\n            return type.cast(closureRepresentation);\\n        }\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1614, "output": 1132, "cacheRead": 40448, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 43194, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777499986904, "responseId": "resp_0f11957e5262e9c20169f27f53a86481a3b8e10a3f542903e1"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_YRMbAOh0BoaObm5V43ijSdmk|fc_0f11957e5262e9c20169f27f5f94dc81a395340c240dfc5144", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2130 bytes to tests/src/com.esotericsoftware/kryo-shaded/3.0.3/src/test/java/com_esotericsoftware/kryo_shaded/ClosureSerializerTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777500001190}]}
